                  "pageTitle": "Energy Inversion",
                  "pageId": 573429,
                  "revisionId": 2600034,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Consistent with Redirection , the increase is applied to the shield capacity of the Archwing after rank bonuses from levelling up the archwing."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Energy Inversion",
                  "pageId": 573429,
                  "revisionId": 2600034,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "For example: If a maxed Energy Inversion is applied to a level 30 Elytron , the Unranked shield capacity (745) is by the +200 bonus shields provided by Elytron being Rank 30 giving 945. This total is multiplied by 2 (+100% Shield bonus from Energy Inversion) for a grand total of 1890."
                }
              }
